WEBVTT

00:00.493 --> 00:02.126
Reid: Previously
on "Criminal Minds"...

00:02.127 --> 00:04.309
My sister and brother-in-law
died in 9/11.

00:04.567 --> 00:07.125
They had a baby girl, Meg.

00:07.127 --> 00:10.486
I took her in. Actually, Chris and I
moved into their house.

00:10.487 --> 00:12.757
She's 13,
and the light of my life.

00:12.759 --> 00:13.909
Make sure you're
home on time,

00:13.911 --> 00:15.381
otherwise the search party's
coming for you.

00:15.383 --> 00:16.566
Meg: Make sure you
text me when you land

00:16.568 --> 00:17.557
or I'll send one
for you.

00:17.559 --> 00:19.190
I love you.
Love you, too.

00:19.192 --> 00:20.246
See you in the morning.

00:20.247 --> 00:21.301
[Computer chimes]

00:21.303 --> 00:23.413
OMG,
he messaged us back.

00:23.415 --> 00:24.533
He is so hot.

00:24.535 --> 00:26.645
Could you imagine if
he was your boyfriend?

00:26.647 --> 00:29.013
He's asking
for a picture.

00:29.015 --> 00:30.837
You're not actually
sending one, are you?

00:30.839 --> 00:32.886
Well, he's a senior.
What's the big deal?

00:35.287 --> 00:36.726
[Camera shutter clicks]

00:42.551 --> 00:44.533
[Ding]

00:48.823 --> 00:50.901
[Woman singing opera]

00:52.000 --> 00:58.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:56.119 --> 01:58.037
[Thump]

02:20.567 --> 02:22.549
[Music stops]

02:22.551 --> 02:24.629
[Muffled sobs]

02:31.255 --> 02:33.333
[Woman sobbing]

03:20.951 --> 03:26.165
♪ I've got a great big
bundle of love ♪

03:26.167 --> 03:27.797
♪ and I have seen this... ♪

03:27.799 --> 03:30.581
How the hell do you think
it makes me feel, huh?

03:30.583 --> 03:32.949
I said I'm sorry.

03:32.951 --> 03:34.901
I bust my butt
at work all day

03:34.903 --> 03:37.429
and all I ask for
is a hot meal.

03:37.431 --> 03:40.629
Honey, I'm sorry,
please.

03:40.631 --> 03:42.869
I know this is
my fault.

03:42.871 --> 03:45.653
You think I want
to do this?

03:45.655 --> 03:49.686
Look, I know you had
a hard day at work.

03:49.687 --> 03:50.773
No!

03:50.775 --> 03:52.437
I had a rough day.

03:52.439 --> 03:54.613
Rough day at work.
Say it right.

03:56.439 --> 03:58.485
I'm sorry.

03:59.735 --> 04:03.061
You had a rough day.

04:03.063 --> 04:06.293
So why do you have to
make it worse?

04:06.295 --> 04:11.349
I'll do better.
I promise.

04:12.535 --> 04:15.477
I'm tired of giving you
second chances.

04:15.479 --> 04:16.661
[Sobbing]

04:16.663 --> 04:18.581
[Screams]

04:18.583 --> 04:20.021
Woman on TV:
...Released a study today

04:20.023 --> 04:22.517
that shows that
supplemental oxygen...

04:24.663 --> 04:25.685
Damn.

04:25.687 --> 04:26.997
You look like you could
use this more than me.

04:26.999 --> 04:28.790
Oh, my hero.

04:28.791 --> 04:30.517
Hey, Meg, let's go!

04:30.519 --> 04:31.701
You're gonna be late
for school.

04:31.703 --> 04:33.013
Meg: Coming.

04:33.015 --> 04:35.893
Thank you.
I saw that.

04:35.895 --> 04:37.557
Good morning
to you, too.

04:37.559 --> 04:40.053
Hey, can I go to the mall
with Markayla

04:40.055 --> 04:41.621
and a couple of other
friends this weekend?

04:41.623 --> 04:43.029
Do these couple of
other friends have names?

04:43.031 --> 04:44.245
Bobby and Tyler.

04:44.247 --> 04:46.293
Ok, those are weird
names for girls.

04:46.295 --> 04:47.765
They're in my biology class.

04:47.767 --> 04:49.877
Ok, well, do these friends know
that Kate has a gun?

04:49.879 --> 04:51.157
You're right.
Hey, stop that.

04:51.159 --> 04:52.821
Technically,
she's got two guns.

04:52.823 --> 04:54.005
[Clears throat]
It's true.

04:54.007 --> 04:56.149
I'm kidding.
Yes, of course you can go.

04:56.151 --> 04:58.709
Thanks, Chris. I need to text Markayla
and let her know.

05:01.751 --> 05:03.765
Ok, what was that?

05:03.767 --> 05:05.237
What?
It's not a date.

05:05.239 --> 05:06.549
She's going to the mall,
it's a public place.

05:06.551 --> 05:08.406
With two boys
that we've never met.

05:08.407 --> 05:09.877
I don't think it's
such a big deal.

05:09.878 --> 05:11.509
We had a plan
for her dating.

05:11.511 --> 05:13.429
This is not a date.

05:13.431 --> 05:16.437
I have 3 guns,
by the way.

05:16.439 --> 05:19.636
Come on, sweetheart.

05:20.503 --> 05:21.717
Over the last 3 weeks,

05:21.719 --> 05:23.797
the bodies of Myia Collins
and Lauren White

05:23.799 --> 05:26.101
have been found in Diamond Bar,
California,

05:26.103 --> 05:28.150
a suburb 25 miles
east of Los Angeles.

05:28.151 --> 05:29.909
Both victims were found
in alley dumpster.

05:29.911 --> 05:32.149
Each had her throat slashed and
had been brutally beaten.

05:32.151 --> 05:34.805
This guy literally
dumped his victims like trash.

05:34.807 --> 05:36.725
Classic misogynist sadist.

05:36.727 --> 05:39.349
Definitely looks like
the torture escalates with each attack.

05:39.351 --> 05:41.653
These women weren't just cut,
they were beaten to a pulp.

05:41.654 --> 05:42.932
That feels personal.

05:42.935 --> 05:44.597
It's possible the unsub
knew both victims,

05:44.599 --> 05:47.989
or at the very least used them as
surrogates for the true object of his anger.

05:47.991 --> 05:49.909
He abducts, offends,
and disposes of each victim

05:49.911 --> 05:51.477
before anyone notices
they're gone.

05:51.479 --> 05:52.853
He may be preying
on loner types.

05:52.855 --> 05:54.485
It looks like they both have
ligature marks

05:54.487 --> 05:55.957
on their wrists
and ankles.

05:55.958 --> 05:57.332
Which means he has
a secure secondary location

05:57.335 --> 05:58.613
where he holds them captive.

05:58.615 --> 06:01.173
So he could be testing
how much torture his victims can take.

06:01.175 --> 06:03.445
And then when he's done with his fun,
if things don't go as planned,

06:03.447 --> 06:05.685
he silences them permanently
by slitting their throats.

06:05.687 --> 06:07.701
The preliminary M.E. report
shows that neither of the victims

06:07.703 --> 06:08.917
were sexually assaulted.

06:08.919 --> 06:09.877
Maybe he's impotent.

06:09.879 --> 06:11.765
Or the abuse is what
really turns him on.

06:11.767 --> 06:13.749
Either way, he's
enjoying their pain.

06:13.751 --> 06:15.637
And he's gonna want to
experience that again.

06:15.639 --> 06:17.685
Wheels up in 30.

06:21.079 --> 06:22.037
[Bang]

06:22.039 --> 06:24.117
[Tape rewinds]

06:27.990 --> 06:31.317
[Bang]

06:31.319 --> 06:32.629
[Tape rewinds]

06:32.631 --> 06:34.837
[Bang]

06:41.719 --> 06:43.509
[Tape rewinds]

06:47.575 --> 06:48.725
[Tape rewinds]

